Golf staff bags are top of the line golf bags like those used by professional golfers. They often have high end finishings like leather construction, a plethora of pockets and storage areas, and large manufacturer logos. They can also be quite heavier than normal
stand bags
or
carry bags
. However, if you aren't walking the course and plan to keep your bag strapped to your cart, then the weight won't be as much of a factor.
GlobalGolf.com carries staff bags from some of the top manufacturers in golf, such as a
TaylorMade staff bag
or a
Titleist staff bag
.

Home of the Best Deals in Golf
For decades, GlobalGolf.com, part of the Worldwide Golf family of brands, has been the leading online destination for golfers of all experience levels who are seeking new and preowned golf gear, accessories and apparel. We provide customers the opportunity to shop both the best deals in golf and the world’s largest selection of preowned clubs, so you can be confident GlobalGolf has all the golf gear you’re looking for at the best possible value!
Satisfaction Guaranteed
At GlobalGolf, we take pride in providing our customers with a world-class shopping experience with outstanding product choices (including the world's largest selection of preowned clubs), friendly and knowledgeable customer service, a fast and reliable delivery process and our renowned 90-Day 100% Satisfaction Guarantee.
Choosing Sustainability
The GlobalGolf business model fosters our ongoing goal of environmental sustainability through the reduction of wasted materials, encourages product reuse, and extends the life of thousands of golf products annually through our Trade-In, Preowned and Second Chance programs.
Services You Want
Additionally, GlobalGolf also offers an innovative selection of services including:
Our Trade-In service
, which lets you trade in your previously played clubs for credit towards your next purchase.
Our Recommendation Tool
, an interactive service that provides you golf gear suggestions from PGA Professionals based on your individual playing style and preferences.
UPerks
®
, our loyalty program that offers rewards every time you shop, trade-in or review a product.
Supporting Golfers for Over 60 Years
Since 1963 we have been there for golfers as the game has grown and evolved and we will continue to be there to help propel golf into the future. Our brand—deeply rooted in golf’s history and the golfing community—extends its reach and impact globally. Operating at a scale that echoes the passion and dedication of golf enthusiasts, we transcend the conventional boundaries of the game. With nearly 100 stores nationwide we have been your local golf shop for decades and generations. Let us help you “Get There”!
Local Retail Stores
With nearly 100 stores in 25+ states, we are one of the largest and fastest growing golf companies in the world.
Online Shopping
Worldwide Golf is an authorized dealer for all major golf brands. We take pride in our huge selection of golf products, apparel and accessories.
WorldwideGolf.com
The world’s largest selection of preowned golf clubs and gear. Check out the best deals in golf.
From the beginner to the seasoned golfer, Fairway Styles offers expertly curated apparel. Always fashionable, never out of bounds.
FairwayStyles.com
Premium Club Fittings
Cool Clubs is a pioneer in custom golf club fitting and building, leveraging proprietary technologies and extensive data to provide golfers with the best possible personalized fits.
CoolClubs.com
Golf Club Rentals
Traveling and Don’t Want to Ship Your Clubs? GetClubs.com will deliver premium rental clubs to any hotel, golf course or staffed business.
GetClubs.com
